      Dear First Name,

      Thank you for considering Relab Real Estate as your partner in the journey to sell your home. We’re excited about the opportunity to work with you and help you achieve the best possible result. Selling a property is more than just a transaction — it’s a significant milestone, and we’re here to ensure the process is smooth, informed, and tailored to your goals.

      In this proposal, you’ll find a comprehensive snapshot of your home’s position in today’s market. We’ve carefully analysed similar properties that have sold recently or are currently listed, combined with current market data, to provide a well-researched estimate of your property’s value.

      To guide you through what comes next, we’ve outlined the key elements involved in preparing, marketing, and selling your property:

      • Property Snapshot – A detailed summary of your home’s standout features and what makes it appealing to buyers.
      • Market Conditions – Insights into what’s happening in the local property market, and how those trends may impact your sale.
      • Comparable Properties – A look at recent and active listings in your area to provide context and perspective on your home’s value.
      • Value Estimate – A professionally informed estimate of your home’s price range based on data and experience.
      • Selling Approach – Strategic recommendations on the most effective sales method for your situation.
      • Marketing Plan – A bespoke marketing strategy to ensure your home gains maximum exposure to the right audience.
      • Where to From Here – An easy-to-follow guide outlining the next steps as we move forward together.

      Our role is to make the process as stress-free and rewarding as possible, by offering honest advice, proactive support, and a strategy designed to help you succeed. We truly value the chance to be part of this important chapter and are committed to delivering outstanding results.

      Kind regards,

      The true value is established when interested buyers compete for your home, driving demand and influencing price. Our role is to ensure your property reaches and resonates with the right audience through a tailored marketing campaign.       Methods of Sale

      Image
      Text

      A fast-paced, deadline-driven method where buyers compete in real time. Auctions create urgency and suit properties in demand or when value is unclear. With no cooling-off period, sales are unconditional, providing certainty for both seller and buyer.

      Text

      Auction

      Text

      Deadline Sale

      Text

      Choosing the right sales method is essential to a successful result. The right approach attracts interest, creates urgency, and drives competition — all of which can help maximise your sale price and streamline the selling process.

      Text

      Fixed Price

      Text

      A straightforward approach where the asking price is set from day one. Buyers know what’s expected, and it typically suits properties in a competitive or price-sensitive market where clarity is key.

      Text

      Tender

      Text

      Buyers submit confidential written offers by a specified deadline, without knowing what others are offering. This process creates a level playing field and suits properties with unique appeal or when discretion is important.

      Text
